Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.04,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我们注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:37.77,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我对运气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.94,0:23:43.03,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}无所指望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:47.68,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:51.66,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.85,0:23:55.20,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}有所准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:02.19,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我将自行斩断退路
